"The language is the heart of our culture"... Robin Wall Kimmerer. 

@agawap this is how we communicate with ALL beings... through Anishnaabemowin...

#BraidingVoicEd

@Drawn2Intellect Even using the word "accountability" related to equity measures causes education systems to be defensive. 

How dare we even ask...

If we are all working in service to students, why would education systems be defensive about accountability measures for such important work.

